body: "GH-602. Shipped .d.ts reference Node globals/modules that only resolve with @types/node, but package declares only typebox in peerDependencies — strict TS consumers get tsc errors from inside node_modules with no guidance. Fix: declare @types/node (peer + peerDependenciesMeta.optional or dep), fix the shipped JSDoc typo/legacy-flag defects, extend packed-tarball TS consumer smoke."
